EQUIX

Swingers

We host events for the sexually liberated.


An exclusive club for members that organizes unique themed events in different cities.


The purpose of the club is to provide a place for fun, smart like-minded people who want to explore all kinds of sexual fantasies.


We like to combine luxury with the environment to create unforgettable experiences.


If you meet the requirements to be accepted as a member, you will be able to access any event of interest to you.



There are only two sacred rules:


1. The privacy of all members, guests and staff must always be respected, therefore recording or taking photographs is strictly prohibited.


2. Strict consent to establish any act with other participants. You ask before you touch.


Anyone who breaks the club rules will be required to leave the event and will lose their membership.


Incomplete or inaccurate applications will not be considered.
